=== onboarding_to_manage_devices_using_defender_for_endpoint ===

--- Join to azure activity directory ---
Accounts > Add a work or school account

--- Microsoft 365 admin center ---
portal.microsoft.com

Billing > Purchase services > Licenses

Microsoft Defender for Endpoint P1
Important
Has less features to P2

--- Features associated to above license ---

--- Onboarding a device onto Defender for Endpoint ---

Grab onboarding script
Place onto onboarding machine
Open cmd as administrator
Run script and input `Y` to confirm onboarding

Check device inventory in portal.microsoft.com

